[[simple:user:immanuelle/Nyakuichi Ōji]] [[simple:User:Immanuelle/Nyakuichi Ōji]] [[sn:Nyakuichi Ōji]] [[sn:yakuichi Ōji]] [[fr:Nyakuichiōji]] [[zh:%E8%8B%A5%E4%B8%80%E7%8E%8B%E5%AD%90]] [[ja:若一王子]] [[fr:Nyakuichi Ōji]] [[fr:User:Immanuelle/Nyakuichi Ōji]] [[en:draft:Nyakuichi Ōji]]
